  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective was to determine the effects of the Gastrointestinal Therapeutic System
      (GITS) formulation of Doxazosin when used in combination therapy with the 5 major classes of
      antihypertensive agents as measure by 24-hour diastolic blood pressure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
